  "content": "<p>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.OiNttXSDW598DIEs]{(Index) Combat Rules}</p>\n<p><strong>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.Q8vJfOFojro5BrWO]{2.06. Combat Modifiers}</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.b7fUAk2heKMPWXZU]{2.06.1. Cover}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.5k8dng1qeuExFjmw]{2.06.2. Concealment}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.L68tjh194oVBMmVL]{2.06.3. Flanking}</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf-content.pf-rules.iC0zWabI6bgxBYg1]{2.06.4. Helpless Defenders}</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>Source&nbsp;PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 195</p>\n<p>A number of factors and conditions can influence an attack roll. Many of these situations grant a bonus or penalty on attack rolls or to a defender&rsquo;s Armor Class.</p>\n<h2>Table 8-5: Attack Roll Modifiers</h2>\n<table style=\"width: 65.726%;\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 65.3903%;\" scope=\"col\">Attacker is...</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 15.1694%;\" scope=\"col\">Melee</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 18.5567%;\" scope=\"col\">Ranged</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 65.3903%;\">Dazzled</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 15.1694%;\">-1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 18.5567%;\">-1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 65.3903%;\">Entangled</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 15.1694%;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 18.5567%;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 65.3903%;\">Flanking defender</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 15.1694%;\">+2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 18.5567%;\">&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 65.3903%;\">Invisible</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 15.1694%;\">+2<sup>2</sup></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 18.5567%;\">+2<sup>2</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 65.3903%;\">On higher ground</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 15.1694%;\">+1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 18.5567%;\">+0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 65.3903%;\">Prone</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 15.1694%;\">-4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 18.5567%;\">&mdash;3</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 65.3903%;\">Shaken or frightened</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 15.1694%;\">-2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 18.5567%;\">-2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 65.3903%;\">Squeezing through a space</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 15.1694%;\">-4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 18.5567%;\">-4</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>1 An entangled character also takes a &ndash;4 penalty to Dexterity, which may affect his attack roll.<br />2 The defender loses any Dexterity bonus to AC.<br />3 Most ranged weapons can&rsquo;t be used while the attacker is prone, but you can use a crossbow or shuriken while prone at no penalty.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Table 8-6: Armor Class Modifiers</h2>\n<table style=\"width: 70.2945%; height: 224px;\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\" scope=\"col\">Defender is...</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\" scope=\"col\">Melee</td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\" scope=\"col\">Ranged</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Behind cover</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Blinded</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Concealed or invisible</td>\n<td style=\"width: 33.5788%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\" colspan=\"2\">See Concealment</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Cowering</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Entangled</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>2</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>2</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Flat-footed</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>1</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>1</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Grappling (but the attacker is not)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0</td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Helpless</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-4<sup>3</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>3</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Kneeling or sitting</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Pinned</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-4<sup>3</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+0<sup>3</sup></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Prone</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Squeezing through a space</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 65.5376%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">Stunned</td>\n<td style=\"width: 14.8748%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n<td style=\"width: 18.704%; height: 16px; text-align: center;\">-2<sup>1</sup></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>1 The defender loses any Dexterity bonus to AC.<br />2 An entangled character takes a &ndash;4 penalty to Dexterity.<br />3 The defender is denied his Dexterity bonus to his Armor Class.</p>"
}
